            "_id": 113062,
            "R": 5,
            "Name": "Denial and Judgment",
            "Desc": "An earring that you picked up in the ruins after completing the duel against The Knave.<br>The red symbol upon it resembles the image in her eyes, a declaration and a rejection alike.<br>The orphaned live lives filled with suffering from childhood — this she sees and keeps in her heart.<br>As fate casts an examining eye on humanity, so too will humans cast judgment upon fate. Someday, honor, injustice, misery, and tears will be denied alongside the old world. Before that moment comes, the last child of the Crimson Moon will record fate's every sin.",
