            "_id": 113056,
            "R": 5,
            "Name": "Lightless Mass",
            "Desc": "A fragment produced from the intense battle against the All-Devouring Narwhal.<br>Even in the dark night sky, there are always faint glimmers of light, like pearls gleaming from within the sand, splinters of diamond sprinkled over asphalt, lights lancing through the fog on a misty night, and sparks that ignite the brightest blazes.<br>But look carefully. The lights are slowly disappearing and the darkness is invading from every direction. You will become an incandescent inferno, a new star burning brightly and illuminating the universe for but a brief period. Or, you will become the ruler of darkness that stamps out all such trifling sparks.",
