            "R": 3,
            "Name": "Remnant Glow of Scorching Might",
            "Desc": "Weapon Ascension Material.<br>To weave together myriad thoughts and reign over countless souls — this is the essence of power.<br>However, power is not cold-blooded tyranny. Its true ideal, at its heart, is to create a utopia free of worry, schemes, and slavery.<br>It was just as the silent lord saw in the crystal's secrets, and just as the lost companion had once taught.<br>The dark insect insignia and the steel judgment thus laid the foundations of the kingdom's rules.",
